kay Chairman Kang.

70
00:04:37.026 --> 00:04:38.111
Sino ang nakakaalam?

71
00:04:38.194 --> 00:04:41.781
Baka tinutulungan ka ni Shin Jung-woo
nang hindi mo alam,

72
00:04:41.864 --> 00:04:43.157
