73
00:04:43.241 --> 00:04:44.575
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

74
00:04:44.659 --> 00:04:45.994
Kailan niya ako tinulungan?

75
00:04:46.661 --> 00:04:48.079
Sinibak siya dahil nag-iisa siyang nagwhistleblowing...

76
00:04:48.162 --> 00:04:48.997
9 NA TAON, 1988

77
00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.456
…sapat na para magpadala ng babala

78
00:04:50.540 --> 00:04:52.625
