Dapat kang magpasalamat
I'm letting you off the hook.

203
00:12:03.764 --> 00:12:05.391
Hindi ako manloloko!

204
00:12:05.474 --> 00:12:08.936
Strictly speaking, hindi pa ako nakapunta
nahuli o naaresto para sa mga ganitong krimen.

205
00:12:09.019 --> 00:12:09.937
bakit naman

206
00:12:10.020 --> 00:12:11.647
Dahil dirty money lang ang hinahabol ko.

207
00:12:11.730 --> 00:12:12.898
Tiyak na ipinagmamalaki mo.

208
00:12:14.358 --> 00:12:16.068
Umalis ka na agad.

209
00:12:16.152 --> 00:12:17.486
Tapos na akong mag-alala sayo.

210
00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:18.404
Jeez!

211
00:12:21.740 --> 00:12:24.285
